---
// Problem Solution section component
---

<!-- Problem-Solution Section -->
<section class="py-24 bg-brand-primary text-brand-text pt-32 pb-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 w-full">
   <div class="pb-32">
      <p class="font-serif text-brand-text text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-6 tracking-tight text-center">
         Every Minute You're Away, Toronto Buyers Are <span class="text-brand-secondary">Choosing Your Competition</span>.</p> 

<p class="text-3xl font-serif max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center"> With $1.1M+ homes selling in days across the GTA, while you're showing properties from King West to Scarborough, qualified buyers are slipping through the cracks straight to agents who respond instantly.
          </p>
   </div>
    
    <!-- Two Column Layout: Problem Left, Solution Right -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-32 items-start">
      
      <!-- LEFT COLUMN: Problem Section -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Problem Image -->
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="https://krzofnafayygoxoinkfv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/4realtyai/page-images/homes.jpg" 
               alt="Real estate agents struggling with slow response times" 
               class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-xl">
        </div>
        
        <!-- Problem Content -->
        <div class="space-y-6 text-brand-text">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-primary text-sm font-sans font-normal bg-red-500 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            Problem
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-medium text-brand-text mb-6 tracking-tight">
            Toronto's Red-Hot Market Demands 24/7 Response Times
          </h2>
          
          
          <!-- Industry Statistics -->
          <div class="">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-sans text-brand-text mb-4">
              GTA Market Statistics:
            </h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <p class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Toronto homes sell 40% faster than Canadian average</span> 
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <p class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">85% of GTA buyers start their search online after 7 PM</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <p class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Mississauga and Brampton agents who respond within 5 minutes are 12x more likely to convert</span> 
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <p class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">The average Toronto agent loses $127,000 annually to delayed lead responses</span> 
                  
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Toronto Market Impact -->
          <div class="rounded-xl p-4 border border-warm-300">
            <p class="font-serif text-sm mb-3">
              <span class="font-semibold">What this means in the Toronto market:</span><br>
              Every hour of delay gives competitors more opportunity to connect with your potential clients first. When Toronto condos average over $820,000 and detached homes average nearly $2 million, even one lost deal represents significant commission.
            </p>
            
            <p class="font-serif italic text-sm">
              How many leads are slipping away while you're busy with other tasks?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: Solution Section -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Solution Image -->
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="https://krzofnafayygoxoinkfv.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/4realtyai/page-images/sandro-schuh-6wVqCeK030Y-unsplash.jpg" 
               alt="Real estate agent successfully using AI technology" 
               class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-xl">
        </div>
        
        <!-- Solution Content -->
        <div class="space-y-6 text-brand-text">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center text-brand-primary text-sm font-sans font-normal bg-green-500 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            Solution
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-medium mb-6 tracking-tight">
            AI Tools Built for Toronto's Unique Real Estate Challenges
          </h2>
          
          
          <!-- Three Benefits Grid -->
          <div class="">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-sans font-medium mb-4">
              What our AI toolkit delivers:
            </h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Never Miss a GTA Lead - </span>
                  <span class="font-normal">24/7 AI assistants capture and qualify prospects</span>
                </h4>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Create Compelling Listings in Seconds - </span>
                  <span class="font-normal">AI writes descriptions that sell</span>
                </h4>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Automate Your Marketing - </span>
                  <span class="font-normal">Social posts, ads, and follow-ups run themselves</span>
                </h4>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                <h4 class="font-sans text-sm">
                  <span class="font-semibold">Client Experience - </span>
                  <span class="font-normal">Deliver the premium service experience that makes clients choose you over every other Toronto agent.</span>
                </h4>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Supporting Quote -->
          <div class="rounded-xl p-4 border border-warm-300">
            <p class="font-serif text-sm mb-3">
              <span class="font-semibold">What this means for you:</span><br>
              You become the dominant Toronto real estate agent in your territory while competitors struggle with outdated manual processes. Every website visitor becomes your lead, every listing showcases your expertise, and every client interaction reinforces why you're Toronto's go-to real estate professional.
            </p>
            
            <p class="font-serif italic text-sm">
              What if you could show properties and close deals while your competitors are still manually responding to emails and creating listings?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>